      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 20:53:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比尔·阿克曼预计特朗普将私有化房利美和房地美</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bill-ackman-expects-trump-privatize-fannie-mae-freddie-mac-2024-12-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁投资者比尔·阿克曼周一表示，他预计美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将解除对房利美和房地美的托管，并可能使它们再次成为私营公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/bill-ackman-expects-trump-privatize-fannie-mae-freddie-mac-2024-12-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 20:14:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银高管在改革前警告不要过度监管银行业</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-boss-warns-against-excessive-banking-regulation-ahead-overhaul-2024-12-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂周一表示，瑞士不应为银行业制定不利于自身的规则，瑞银集团收购瑞士信贷后，瑞士正准备对监管进行彻底改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-boss-warns-against-excessive-banking-regulation-ahead-overhaul-2024-12-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 12:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
